Unnamed: 2: Data refers to the 12 months ending January 1 of each year, covers Australia based team members only, and is consistent with our Workplace Gender Equality Agency (WGEA) submissions. F21 figures have been re-stated to exclude Endeavour Group.

The ratios reported are relative to the total average salary within the managerial and managerial categories, irrespective of role and position level (ie, not like-for-like). Through our ongoing Pay Parity Project, we monitor the gender pay gap for like-for-like roles across the Woolworths Group, at all levels. Our last review confirmed a gap of less than 1%, which we aim to maintain.

Data refers to financial years and covers all Australian Food, Corporate and New Zealand operations. F23 data excludes PFD Foods and MyDeal, while F21 data includes Endeavour Group. We are working towards a resolution on all outstanding claims.

Data refers to financial years, covers all Australian and New Zealand headcount, and excludes workforce located in Greater China, Bangladesh, The Philippines and Thailand. F21 figures have been re-stated to exclude Endeavour Group.
